This kit is designed to provide an out-of-the-box experience for working with Azure logs.

An integration guide is available on [this documentation page](https://docs.gravwell.io/integrations/cloud/azure.html)

This kit provides the following utilities:

- Queries
    - Detections
    - Stats
- Dashboards
- Actionables
- Templates
- Macros

Refer to Kit Overview playbook for more detail on these components.

## Version History
**V1: Initial Release**